    gtk: skip keyboard grab when hover autograb is active
    
    It's pointless.  With grab on hover enabled the keyboard grab
    is already active when you press Ctrl-Alt-G ;)
    
    Signed-off-by: Gerd Hoffmann <kraxel@redhat.com>

